  "remarks": "IRe.036. Designation: KAA is an IRGC-owned company involved in large scale civil and military construction projects and other engineering activities. It undertakes a significant amount of work on Passive Defense Organization projects. In particular, KAA subsidiaries were heavily involved in the construction of the uranium enrichment site at Qom/Fordow.; Listing: Listed by the 1737 Committee on 9 June 2010 (amended on 17 December 2014).",
